data.description: Lovely 3/2 Single family home at Gated community at Vizcaya! Recently painted, new roof, new air conditioner unit and kitchen upgraded with stainless steel appliances .Great views from master bedroom and living room to the lake. Two car garage. Tile and wood floors throughout. This gated community offer many amenities : Clubhouse, Fitness Center ,Children’s playground, Swimming pool, gated community ,24 hour security .This property is located in top rated school area.
